window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nevin Goosemen has lost everything: his career as a politician, his magitech army, and his reputation. He’s very, very angry at the Dragon Elite, and he’s going to try and make them pay with their lives. </p> <p>The Dragon Elite have had their fair share of enemies, but no one like this. Nevin Goosemen isn’t going to rest until he’s destroyed every single dragon and rider. </p> <p>It’ll be a race to protect the demon dragons before it’s too late. The Dragon Elite might have just won a battle, but in doing so, they started a war. </p> <p>Can Sophia Beaufont lead the Dragon Elite to victory?</p>"; 
